<div class="title">First Experience Ever!</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=MysteryMatt&Exact=1">MysteryMatt</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; MysteryMatt. "First Experience Ever!: An Experience with 2C-B (exp39513)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 12, 2008. erowid.org/exp/39513</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

